Discussion Board

We have a discussion board available on GitHub for #rstats related questions, posts, discussions and announcements.

To join, request access to GitHub TampaUseRs organization by sending your GitHub username to @UseRTampa on Twitter or the TampaUseRs organizers via email or Meetup. The discussion board is under Teams > Everyone > Discussion.

Upcoming Meetups

Social Network Analysis!

Tuesday, Jul 24, 2018 at 07:00pm

Southern Brewing & Winemaking
4500 North Nebraska Avenue, Tampa
https://www.meetup.com/Tampa-R-Users-Group/events/252637314/

What we'll do
Thomas Keller will walk us through social network analysis of Twitter data using rtweet and tidy principles.

What to bring
If you wish to bring a laptop to follow along, code and slides will be posted ~24 hours in advance at https://github.com/TampaUseRs/TampaUseRs/tree/master/meetups

Speaker Resources

Are you interested in speaking at an upcoming Tampa R Users Group Meetup? If so, please drop a line to us at UseRTampa at gmail dot com or via our Meetup page.

For upcoming speakers, weve compiled a list of resources and materials to help you plan, design, and promote your talk. Visit the TampaUseRs/speaker-starter-kit repository on GitHub for more information. We cant wait to learn from you!
